<div style="padding: 20px;">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666;"><u>Un nouveau message a été envoyé via le formulaire de contact</u> :</p>
  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #333;">
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; width: 120px; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">Nom :</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #666;">{{ contact_name }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #333">
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">Email :</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #666;">{{ contact_email }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #333">
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">Motif :</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #666;">{{ contact_reason }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #333">
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">Sujet :</td>
      <td style="padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #D3D3D3; color: #666;">{{ contact_subject }}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <div style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #333;">Message :</h2>
    <p style="margin: 0; color: #666;">{{ contact_message }}</p>
  </div>
</div>
